{"tid":2296954,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"深秋首轉涼！天文台料下周一跌至17°C 北區14°C","createTime":"2020-11-23T02:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T04:49:36.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d7efd57d2a497920757144cf33da87bfb6980d97","tid":2296954,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:03:14.000Z","msg":"臨近11月尾，香港將迎接深秋首次轉涼！本港昨日（22日）經歷60年來最熱的「小雪」後，天文台預計，一股東北季候風的補充在周末期間抵港，周六起一連4日乾燥，相當濕度均低見45%，周末至下周初的氣溫亦逐步下降；市區氣溫會由周五最高的27&deg;C，跌至下周一最低的17&deg;C，或再創9月入秋以來最低溫，也將是入秋後首次跌至清涼水平（12.5至17.5&deg;C）。而由天文台超級電腦直接輸出、未經人手修正的分區氣溫預報指，北區的打鼓嶺在下周一早上跌至13.7&deg;C，相當清涼。<br />\n<br />\n雖然昨日是二十四節氣之一的「小雪」，東北季候風亦持續吹送本港，但由於天色大致良好，大量日照令氣溫上升，尖沙嘴天文台總部昨午錄得最高28.2&deg;C，是60年來最熱的「小雪」，打平1960年的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OrxjXFygTKHzoW_F-cHfpmL37NY=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YO4TZNQEWBATTEZYRQ5E6DLCU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOrxjXFygTKHzoW_F-cHfpmL37NY%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYO4TZNQEWBATTEZYRQ5E6DLCU4.jpg&h=9ebc5a57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"060bd8fac95f33119857fbc221d5378807686a79","tid":2296954,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:06:45.000Z","msg":"又話全球暖化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b1526a9db4721c8610ef112d288dbfe18eb9fe","tid":2296954,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:26:28.000Z","msg":"凍到要射波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef046c48fde5bf4b5472cf6d32720927d2d295ed","tid":2296954,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"060bd8fac95f33119857fbc221d5378807686a79","tid":2296954,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:06:45.000Z","msg":"又話全球暖化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"全球暖化帶來極端天氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b56dfe1f594f2548200ca4bf9479e0f892ca9b1","tid":2296954,"uid":361657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"060bd8fac95f33119857fbc221d5378807686a79","tid":2296954,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:06:45.000Z","msg":"又話全球暖化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:18:06.000Z","msg":"依我理解既話就係因為全球暖化先會變成咁"},{"pid":"3ba0f5880d7e1d5066b1b7dc2420f7ecf5da554e","tid":2296954,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"朝早可能涼，跟住熱足全日"}]}